INNER JOIN (

    FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
    WHERE (([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t0] ON [d].[DishId] = [t0].[DishId]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [t0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)

    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CategoriesId], [d0].[Code], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Description], [d0].[Name], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[Price]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d0]

) AS [t] ON [d].[DishId] = [t].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
2019-10-18 19:44:10.206 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__daydate_1='?' (DbType = Date), @__companyid_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__userId_2='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [t].[DishId], [t].[IngredientId], [t].[Id], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Name]
FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [i].[Id], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[Name]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN [Ingredients] AS [i] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [i].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
ORDER BY [d].[Id], [t].[DishId], [t].[IngredientId], [t].[Id]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)

    ORDER BY [d].[Name]
) AS [t]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [i].[Id], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

SELECT [c].[Code], [c].[Name], [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Name], [t1].[c], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]
FROM [Categories] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Date], [d0].[DishId], [d0].[CompanyId]
        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t] ON [d].[Id] = [t].[DishId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
        FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
        WHERE ((([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[UserId] = @__userId_2) AND @__userId_2 IS NOT NULL)) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[Id] = [t0].[DishId]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CategoriesId]
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Date], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[CompanyId]

    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Name], CASE
        WHEN (([t0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND ([t0].[Date] IS NOT NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)) OR ([t0].[Date] IS NULL AND @__daydate_1 IS NULL) THEN [t0].[Quantity]
        ELSE 0
    END AS [c], [d].[PictureId], [d].[CategoriesId], [t].[Date], [t].[DishId], [t].[CompanyId]

        FROM [DayDish] AS [d0]
        WHERE (([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d0].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)

     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]

    )
)

) AS [t] ON [d].[DishId] = [t].[Id]

    FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]

SELECT [a].[Id] AS [UserId], MIN([a].[NormalizedUserName]) AS [UserName], @__daydate_1 AS [Date], COUNT(*) AS [DishesCount], SUM(CAST([t0].[Quantity] AS decimal(18,2)) * [t].[Price]) AS [Amount]
FROM [DayDish] AS [d]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CategoriesId], [d0].[Code], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Description], [d0].[Name], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[Price]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d0]
    WHERE ([d0].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL
) AS [t] ON [d].[DishId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [u].[UserId], [u].[Date], [u].[DishId], [u].[CompanyId], [u].[Quantity]
    FROM [UserDayDish] AS [u]
    WHERE (([u].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([u].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
) AS [t0] ON [d].[DishId] = [t0].[DishId]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [t0].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
WHERE (([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyid_0) AND @__companyid_0 IS NOT NULL) AND (([d].[Date] = @__daydate_1) AND @__daydate_1 IS NOT NULL)
GROUP BY [a].[Id]
